From: <ops@gssshipping-eg.com>
To: thalassini@vessels.astraship.com
Cc: "'Operations - Astra Shipmanagement Inc'" <ops@astraship.com>,greece@gssshipping-eg.com,Suezcanal@gssshipping-eg.com,Accounts@gssshipping-eg.com
Date: Sat, 03/May/2025 17:23:09 (UTC: +03:00)
Subject: M/V THALASSINI | VOY.51 | SUEZ CANAL TRANSIT I CTM
Attachments(1): image001.png

To: Master of MV THALASSINI

Cc: Astra Shipmanagement Inc

Fm: GSS Shipping Agencies Egypt

 

Dear Captain

Good day

 

We have the pleasure attending your good vessel as owners protecting agent during vessel upcoming to Suez Canal performing delivery CTM 30,000,00 USD.

Therefore Please advise us the required denominations for the CTM order liaising with our bank in due time and depending of the denomination’s availability.

 

 

Thanks In Advance & Best Regards

 

Tamer Antar | Managing Director 

 

GSS SHIPPING AGENCIES (EGYPT)

Address: 23rd Of July Street, Alaa Tower.

Port Said – Egypt

Mob No: +201226180464
